{"word":"ἐκπληρόω","slug":"ἐκπληρόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκπληρόω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ώσω,  ἐκπίμπλημι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to fill quite up</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to make up</i> to a certain number, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to man completely</i>, <el>ναῦς</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><i>to fulfil</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>ἐκπλ. λιμένα</el> <i>to make one's way over</i> the harbour, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>emetiri</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}